Name: Sword Rogue
About the game: The game is a really simple rogue like game, (basically because the developer is unable to draw any complex figures). In the game you just walk around with a sword in the hand and try to reach as high level as you can. Please do contact me if you encountered any bug or have some ideas about how to improve this game. Beautiful skill icons drawn by @Kellon!.
